manify.utils.dataloaders.load(name, **kwargs)

Driver function to load the specified dataset

Parameters:

  • name (str) – The name of the dataset in string.

  • **kwargs – Additional keyword argument.

Return type:

Tuple[Float[Tensor, 'nodes nodes'], Float[Tensor, 'nodes'], Float[Tensor, 'nodes nodes']]

Returns:

A tuple that contains the distance matrix, the labels, and the adjacency matrix
